    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Yes. In this dataset:\n",
        "\n",
        "Item_price is likely right-skewed (some items are much costlier).\n",
        "\n",
        "Features like price_csat_interaction or category_avg_csat may have different scales.\n",
        "\n",
        "Some algorithms (like Logistic Regression, KNN, SVM) perform better when data is scaled or normalized."
      ],
      "metadata": {
