    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Yes, dimensionality reduction can be useful in this project if:\n",
        "\n",
        "You have a large number of features (like category_1 to category_9, many Sub-category_x, etc.).\n",
        "\n",
