      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "1.Accuracy\n",
        "What it means:\n",
        "Percentage of total correct predictions made by the model.\n",
        "\n",
        "Business impact:\n",
        "High accuracy means the model is reliably predicting customer satisfaction, helping the company identify service trends and overall performance.\n",
        " But alone, accuracy might be misleading if classes are imbalanced.\n",
        "\n",
        "=>2. Precision\n",
        "What it means:\n",
        "Out of all the instances predicted as high satisfaction (e.g., CSAT = 5), how many were actually correct?\n",
        "\n",
        "Business impact:\n",
        "High precision reduces false positives—this is critical for ensuring that positive feedback isn’t overestimated.\n",
        "It helps management avoid overconfidence in team performance and take action only when customer feedback is truly positive.\n",
        "\n",
        "=>3. Recall\n",
        "What it means:\n",
        "Out of all actual high satisfaction cases, how many did the model identify?\n",
        "\n",
        "Business impact:\n",
        "High recall ensures that most satisfied customers are captured.\n",
        "It helps Flipkart measure true success rate of customer service efforts and make sure positive experiences aren’t missed in analysis.\n",
        "\n",
        "=>4. F1-Score\n",
        "What it means:\n",
        "Harmonic mean of precision and recall — balances both metrics.\n",
        "\n",
        "Business impact:\n",
        "F1-Score provides a more realistic measure when there's class imbalance (e.g., fewer CSAT=1 vs CSAT=5).\n",
        "It gives an overall business view of model performance, helping balance between acting on feedback and not overreacting.\n",
        "\n",
        "=> Overall Business Impact of the Model:\n",
        "Identifies which agents or shifts are underperforming.\n",
        "\n",
        "Enables targeted training and process improvements.\n",
        "\n",
        "Supports better resource allocation and customer experience strategies.\n",
        "\n",
        "Reduces churn and improves customer loyalty."
